"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367784b86ae877e589eaa85c57d45aae0db41361","tid":2058104,"uid":134103,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"06494b65188c7efb90d9cba2c24bab6ce94cf2d3","tid":2058104,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b7f7dba9668204ed4a384a60bfbd8239f39718c","tid":2058104,"uid":134103,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:19:01.000Z","msg":"樣衰就一直都知，但係feel到自己係毒撚係入U之後先明顯察覺得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"點解入U先知<br />\n<br />\n即係覺得自己好摺?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"係呀，入U之後有試過上莊住Hall，但係成日都覺得自己同身邊新識嘅朋友格格不入，問題係出自我身上，因為佢哋都好nice，係唔知點解我唔係咁想群埋佢哋一大班人一齊玩，寧願自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇上莊冇住Hall之後開始獨來獨往，日日都係自己返學，食Lunch，放學，食Tea，初時都覺得有啲寂寞，會諗其實會唔會只係嗰班人同我唔夾，我應該試下識一班新朋友呢？<br />\n<br />\n但係過多排我開始習慣自己一個，仲覺得其實都幾舒服，自己一個唔使成日講嘢，得閒就去拉吧瞓覺，一係就去行下U附近嘅地方，搵下有咩好嘢食，其實都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到依家就快grad，我仲係一個朋友都識唔到，但係我覺得自己都算過得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過我比較擔心識唔到人冇人脈，遲下踏入社會工作會好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69676db7e922f9617ed18de6c1930a694b476d3","tid":2058104,"uid":260328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自問樣子OK 正常, 有女朋友, 番工同同事吹水冇問題,對住老細都可以正常對答present , 同同事都多話題, (時不時收工都會一齊食飯) 不過收工之後有時會想自己一個人靜一靜或者gym, 有時sales 過黎煩我, 會覺得佢地好煩, 頭一次唔識拒絕, 俾人煩左成個鐘, 之後先識唔好理佢地, (但內心又好中二咁想大大聲屌9佢地, 不過唔敢得罪人)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同中同好耐冇見, 好似個圈子得番番工同事同女朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都唔知自己係味毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710aa9eb782dbde4dd01f6481e0d9831a5d9793f","tid":2058104,"uid":334761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"中一就知自己係毒撚"},{"pid":"47eb4a6ecb036558b205999da9d4ca4b40705a6c","tid":2058104,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a69676db7e922f9617ed18de6c1930a694b476d3","tid":2058104,"uid":260328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自問樣子OK 正常, 有女朋友, 番工同同事吹水冇問題,對住老細都可以正常對答present , 同同事都多話題, (時不時收工都會一齊食飯) 不過收工之後有時會想自己一個人靜一靜或者gym, 有時sales 過黎煩我, 會覺得佢地好煩, 頭一次唔識拒絕, 俾人煩左成個鐘, 之後先識唔好理佢地, (但內心又好中二咁想大大聲屌9佢地, 不過唔敢得罪人)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同中同好耐冇見, 好似個圈子得番番工同事同女朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都唔知自己係味毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"唔會屌<br />\n<br />\n會撚鳩佢地"},{"pid":"9d83e8189e2feb258ce6f4970c244b4e78f99b48","tid":2058104,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0598d51b08d4582042b170ef2a93a117ccc892b","tid":2058104,"uid":134103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a69676db7e922f9617ed18de6c1930a694b476d3","tid":2058104,"uid":260328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.